\c 4
\nb
\v 1 Wasesenza ilathi lethusi, ubude balo buzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili, lobubanzi balo buzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili, lokuphakama kwalo kuzingalo ezilitshumi\x + 7.7. 8.12. 15.8. 1 Kho. 8.64. 2 Kho. 16.14. Eks. 27.1-5. Hez. 43.13-16.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Wasesenza ulwandle olubunjwe ngokuncibilikisa, luzingalo ezilitshumi kusukela okhunjini lwalo kusiya okhunjini lwalo, lwalugombolozele inhlangothi zonke, lokuphakama kwalo kuzingalo ezinhlanu, lomzila wezingalo ezingamatshumi amathathu ulugombolozele inhlangothi zonke\x + 1 Kho. 7.23-26.\x*.
\v 3 Lokufanana kwenkabi kwakungaphansi kwalo, kubhodabhoda inhlangothi zonke zalo, ezilitshumi engalweni, lugombolozela ulwandle inhlangothi zonke; imizila emibili yenkabi yabunjwa ngokuncibilikisa ekubunjweni kwalo\x + 1 Kho. 7.24.\x*.
\v 4 Lwalumi phezu kwenkabi ezilitshumi lambili; ezintathu zikhangele enyakatho, lezintathu zikhangele entshonalanga, lezintathu zikhangele eningizimu, lezintathu zikhangele empumalanga; lolwandle lwaluphezu kwazo phezulu, lazo zonke ingemuva zazo zazingaphakathi.
\v 5 Uhlonzi lwalo lwaluyibubanzi besandla, lomphetho walo wawunjengomsebenzi womphetho wenkezo, \add njeng\add*eluba lomduze, lwalumumethe \w amabhathi\w**, lumumethe azinkulungwane ezintathu\x + 1 Kho. 7.26.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Wasesenza inditshi zokugezela ezilitshumi, wabeka ezinhlanu ngakwesokunene, lezinhlanu ngakwesokhohlo, ukugezisela kizo; babegezisela kizo okomnikelo wokutshiswa; kodwa ulwandle lwalungolwabapristi ukugezela kulo.
\v 7 Wasesenza izinti zezibane zegolide ezilitshumi njengokumiswa kwazo, wazibeka ethempelini, ezinhlanu ngakwesokunene, lezinhlanu ngakwesokhohlo.
\v 8 Wenza lamatafula alitshumi, wawabeka ethempelini, amahlanu ngakwesokunene, lamahlanu ngakwesokhohlo. Wenza lemiganu elikhulu yegolide.
\v 9 Wenza leguma labapristi leguma elikhulu, lezivalo zeguma, wazihuqa izivalo zalo ngethusi.
\v 10 Wasebeka ulwandle ehlangothini lokunene ngasempumalanga maqondana leningizimu.
\p
\v 11 UHuramu wasesenza izimbiza lamafotsholo lemiganu yokufafaza\x + 1 Kho. 7.40-51.\x*. UHuramu waqeda ukwenza umsebenzi ayewenzela inkosi uSolomoni endlini kaNkulunkulu.
\v 12 Insika ezimbili, lemiganu, leziduku phezu kwengqonga yezinsika ezimbili, lamambule amabili okwembesa imiganu emibili yeziduku ezaziphezu kwengqonga yezinsika\x + 1 Kho. 7.41,42.\x*,
\v 13 \w lamapomegranati\w** angamakhulu amane emambuleni womabili, imizila emibili yamapomegranati kulelo lalelombule\x + 1 Kho. 7.42. 1 Kho. 7.20.\x*, okwembesa imiganu emibili yeziduku ezaziphezu\f + \fk phezu: \fl Heb. \fq phambi.\f* kwengqonga yezinsika\x + 1 Kho. 7.41,42.\x*.
\v 14 Wenza lezisekelo, wenza lezinditshi zokugezela phezu kwezisekelo\x + 1 Kho. 7.27,38.\x*;
\v 15 ulwandle olulodwa, lezinkabi ezilitshumi lambili ngaphansi kwalo.
\v 16 Lezimbiza, lamafotsholo, lamafologwe\x + 1 Lan. 28.17.\x*, lazo zonke izitsha zakho uHuramu Abhi wazenzela inkosi uSolomoni esenzela indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngethusi elikhazimulayo\x + 1 Kho. 7.14.\x*.
\v 17 Inkosi yazibumbela ngokuncibilikisa emagcekeni eJordani emhlabathini olibumba phakathi kweSukothi leZeredatha\x + Hlu. 7.22. 1 Kho. 7.46. 11.26.\x*.
\v 18 USolomoni wasezenza zonke lezizitsha ngobunengi obukhulu, ngoba isisindo sethusi sasingehlolwe\x + 1 Kho. 7.47.\x*.
\p
\v 19 USolomoni wazenza-ke zonke izitsha ezazingezendlu kaNkulunkulu, lelathi legolide, lamatafula okwakukhona kuwo izinkwa zokubukiswa\x + 4.8.\x*,
\v 20 lezinti zezibane lezibane zazo ngegolide elicwengekileyo\x + 1 Kho. 6.20.\x*, ukuthi zibhebhe ngokwesimiso\x + 4.7.\x* phambi kwendawo yelizwi\x + 1 Kho. 6.5.\x*;
\v 21 lamaluba lezibane lezindlawu, ngegolide, kwakuligolide elipheleleyo;
\v 22 lezindlawu, lemiganu yokufafaza, lezinkezo, lezitsha zokuthwala umlilo, ngegolide elicwengekileyo\x + 1 Kho. 6.20.\x*; njalo iminyango yendlu, izivalo zayo ezingaphakathi, ezengcwele yezingcwele, lezivalo zendlu yethempeli zazingezegolide\x + 1 Kho. 7.50.\x*.
